{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Raheir rushes forward aggressively, dealing {if:SF_9}{c_number}{payload:CHARGE_PAYLOAD}{/c}{else}heavy{/if} Physical damage and Taunting nearby enemies for {c_number}{SF_4}{/c} seconds.

Selecting a Mercenary Core Skill alters their wielded Weapon and Basic Attack.
{c_label}Weapon:{/c} {c_important}Tower Shield{/c}
{c_label}Basic Attack:{/c} {c_important}Shield Bash{/c}
Raheir bashes enemies with a tower shield, dealing {if:SF_9}{c_number}{payload:MELEE_PAYLOAD_TOOLTIP}{/c}{else}moderate{/if} Physical damage and {c_important}{u}Fortifying{/u}{/c} you for {c_number}[{SF_6}*100]%{/c} of your Maximum Life.
